dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: GEE, IF YOU'RE THE RULER OF "HECK" YOU MUST HAVE SOME KIND OF AWESOME NAME.

dialogue.speaker: Dilbert
dialogue.text: WELL, WHAT IS IT? SOMETHING LIKE "KING OF EVIL" OR "LORD OF DARKNESS"?

dialogue.speaker: Unknown
dialogue.text: YOU CAN CALL ME PHIL, PRINCE OF INSUFFICIENT LIGHT.
